column2: Assuming operation in a browser, a standardized and dev friendly API, and a click is made to `#button` in the HTML, what is printed to console.log? Example<title> </head> <body> <div> <button id="button">Click</button> </div> <script> document.body.addEventListener("click", function(e) { console.log(e.target.tagName); }); </script> </body> </html>
